channel.title: Someone please help me!
channel.description: I just got my account disabled after I connection losted, and this has happened before, and I do not know why. I was not doing anything bad, not even talking, actually, and after I connection lost, I try to log back in, and it's disabled.. how do I get it enabled again?[br][size=1]Posted on: February 01, 2007, 11:03:11 PM[/size][hr]To be honest, it would be incredibley helpful if anyone could even tell me why this is happening.[br][size=1]Posted on: February 01, 2007, 11:05:13 PM[/size][hr]Omg, I know someone has to know what to do.. or what is making it do this.. it's my first day.. and I haven't learned EVERYTHING yet.

you cant get your account back if it says your account has been disabled check message centre for details if it says that or something like that just make a new account you cant get it back unless its not a perm bann.
